Author: iwanttobedainty
Text: Yesss this happens to me all the time.

Author: ak528015
Text: this happens to me too. i’m not sure if it’s guilt or an actual physical reaction but probably a combination of both.  i fasted for a few days before giving into a popeyes chicken sandwich. a few bites in i started to feel sick to my stomach. i wasn’t even enjoying the taste but of course i still ate the rest of it, which led to intense stomach cramps and a trip to the bathroom (TMI, sorry).  if i break a fast with something lighter (a salad, veggies, etc.) i’m *usually* okay, but after fasting or restricting heavy and then eating fast food/junk food, i always feel awful.
